column16: David Eckstein out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Mike Cameron.    Oscar Salazar scores.
Tony Gwynn singles on a line drive to center fielder Mike Cameron.    Oscar Salazar to 3rd.    Tony Gwynn to 2nd on the throw.
Oscar Salazar doubles (2) on a line drive to right fielder Corey Hart.    Everth Cabrera scores.
Everth Cabrera singles on a ground ball to pitcher Tim Dillard.  Everth Cabrera advances to 2nd, on missed catch error by first baseman Prince Fielder.
Ryan Zimmerman grounds out, third baseman Casey McGehee to first baseman Prince Fielder.
Cristian Guzman homers (5) on a fly ball to center field.   Wil Nieves scores.    Ronnie Belliard scores.
Ronnie Belliard singles on a line drive to left fielder Ryan Braun.    Wil Nieves to 2nd.
Alberto Gonzalez flies out to left fielder Ryan Braun.
Willie Harris grounds out, first baseman Prince Fielder to pitcher Tim Dillard.
Josh Willingham lines out to center fielder Mike Cameron.
Tim Dillard intentionally walks Adam Dunn.
Ryan Zimmerman grounds out softly, third baseman Casey McGehee to first baseman Prince Fielder.    Cristian Guzman to 2nd.
Nyjer Morgan grounds into double play, second baseman Felipe Lopez to first baseman Prince Fielder.    Collin Balester out at 2nd.
Collin Balester singles on a ground ball to center fielder Mike Cameron.
Wil Nieves grounds out, shortstop J.   Hardy to first baseman Prince Fielder.
Alberto Gonzalez grounds into double play, third baseman Casey McGehee to second baseman Felipe Lopez to first baseman Prince Fielder.    Willie Harris out at 2nd.
Willie Harris walks.    Adam Dunn to 3rd.    Josh Willingham to 2nd.
Josh Willingham singles on a line drive to left fielder Ryan Braun.    Adam Dunn to 2nd.
Ryan Zimmerman grounds out, third baseman Casey McGehee to first baseman Prince Fielder.
